data.description: Cute home located near schools and parks!  Come check out this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in Blackfoot.  It has so many neat features! It's well cared for and ready for new owners.  The main level has 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a spacious living room and a clean kitchen.  The basement is set up for a large family room and a master suite with a large bedroom and closet plus its own bathroom!  You'll love the fence in the back yard, plus it has a 1 car garage.  Don't miss the solid exterior with vinyl siding and windows!
